import { Navbar, Nav, Container, Image } from "react-bootstrap";
import { HeaderProps } from "modules/Header/types";
import logo from "assets/images/klipartz 1.png";

import Text from "components/Text/Text";
import { NavStyled } from "modules/Header/Headerstyled";

const Header = ({ children }: HeaderProps): any => {
	return (
		<header>
			<Navbar expand='lg' collapseOnSelect>
				<Container>
					<Navbar.Brand href='/'>
						<Image src={logo}></Image>
					</Navbar.Brand>
					<Navbar.Toggle aria-controls='basic-navbar-nav' />
					<Navbar.Collapse id='basic-navbar-nav'>
						<NavStyled className='ml-auto'>
							<Nav.Link href='/home'>
								<Text variant='p2'>Home</Text>
							</Nav.Link>
							<Nav.Link href='/catalog'>
								<Text variant='p2'>Catalog</Text>
							</Nav.Link>
							<Nav.Link href='/contacts'>
								<Text variant='p2'>Contacts</Text>
							</Nav.Link>
							<Nav.Link href='/delivery'>
								<Text variant='p2'>Delivery</Text>
							</Nav.Link>
							<Nav.Link href='/stores'>
								<Text variant='p2'>Stores</Text>
							</Nav.Link>
							<Nav.Link href='/search'></Nav.Link>
							<Nav.Link href='/cart'></Nav.Link>
							<Nav.Link href='/favorites'></Nav.Link>
						</NavStyled>
					</Navbar.Collapse>
				</Container>
			</Navbar>
		</header>
	);
};

export default Header;
